72  def callback(self, data):
73  """ speech recognition response callback """
74  action = data.action
75  target = data.target
76  try:
77  set_skills = self.kb_interface.check_syntax(action, target)
78  skill = self.kb_interface.check_semantic(action, target, set_skills)
79  steps, constraints = self.kb_interface.retrieve_actions(skill)
80  self.kb_interface.procedural_attachment(steps, target)
81  print "Constraints : {}".format(constraints)
82  self.planner.initialize(steps, constraints)
83  client = actionlib.SimpleActionClient('task_action', ExecuteTaskAction)
84  client.wait_for_server()
85  client.send_goal(ExecuteTaskGoal(order=skill), self.ending_callback, self.activation_callback, self.actuator_callback)
86  except (RequestSyntax_Error, TargetUnknown_Error) as e:
87  self.speak(e.message)
88  Reasoning.unknown_symbol_publisher.publish(String(e.value))
89  except Exception as e:
